WEBVTT

14:07.070 --> 14:08.470 line:80%
Thank you for the compliment.

14:08.470 --> 14:09.530 line:80%
No need to thank me.

14:10.190 --> 14:11.470 line:80%
From today on,

14:11.640 --> 14:13.470 line:80%
we must stick together.

14:13.590 --> 14:15.280 line:80%
Show those gossips

14:15.430 --> 14:18.290 line:80%
that we young women are
also capable of great deeds!
